.TH UNICODE 1 "2003-01-31"
.SH NAME
unicode \- command line unicode database query tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B unicode
.RI [ options ]
string
.SH DESCRIPTION
This manual page documents the
.B unicode
command.
.PP
\fBunicode\fP is a command line unicode database query tool.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h
.B \-\-help

Show help and exit.

.TP
.B \-x
.B \-\-hexadecimal

Assume
.I string
to be a hexadecimal number

.TP
.B \-d
